Dearest Frederic

.ue 2
                                                                       $.#$
Forts.: <2 Jan 65>*
It was right you wrote to us soon I thank you, whenever you write tell us
wether David is well. tell papa all about you when he comes to Stutg. how
you feel with tante and your new home, Also about the tea and merredig.
Send me plenty news about you and the whole house.

Mr Wrz paid us a visit yesterday wishing us a good new year; he sends you
love. Nathanael Weitbrecht came yesterday evening they are much grieved
about dear Scheffel. Martha has gone to Bale and will perhaps return after
a few weeks with Marie and the child.

Give my love to dear Mama to dear tante and all the dear people by you Are
you well
.fo -
                                yours JG



